SIMPLE: physically
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Physically
<hw>Phys"ic*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a physical manner;
according to the laws of nature or physics; by physical force; not
morally.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I am not now treating <qex>physically</qex> of light or
colors.</q> <rj><qau>Locke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>According to the rules of medicine.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He that lives <qex>physically</qex> must live miserably.</q>
<rj><qau>Cheyne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>physicalness</ent>
